iteris  wikipedia iteris from wikipedia the free encyclopedia   redirected from iteris inc jump to navigation search iteris inc type public traded as nasdaq iti industry communication equipment founded  headquarters santa ana california united states area served worldwide key people joe bergera chief executive officer president director andy schmidt chief financial officer as of december  update products intelligent transportation systems revenue  m as of december  update number of employees  as of december  update website wwwiteriscom iteris inc is an american company which was set up in  and now is based in santa ana california focusing on intelligent information solutions to the traffic management market globally based on its technology these intelligent transportation systems its help to reduce traffic congestions improve predictions of weather and traffic conditions and provide more accurate performance analysis there are two major segments in iteris namely roadway sensors and transportation systems in december  the company acquired meridian environmental technology inc in november  the company acquired berkeley transportation systems inc contents  history  products  research and development  awards  references  external links historyedit in the late s iteris acquired some assets of rockwell international corp mohaddes associates and viggen corporation meanwhile it cooperated to develop a lane departure warning system in  iteris reconstructed its production line of lane departure to be an intelligent traffic management information company and then developed the iperform group after that the company acquired meridian environmental technologies and berkeley transportation systems for better weather forecasting and traffic measurement productsedit iteris inc’s roadway sensors segment markets on vehicle detection systems for traffic intersection control and traffic data collections the products of this segment are vantage series video detection system such as vantageview vantage vector smartspan and smartcycle versicam pico and abacus the company’s transportation systems segment markets on transportation engineering and consulting services information systems and decision support systems for better traffic conditions in addition its iperform segment markets on transportation performance measurement in  the company launched smartcycle which can detect vehicles and bicycles accurately with a single video detection camera facing a dedicated approach in  the company launched pedtrax which automates measurement of both the count direction and speed of pedestrians in crosswalks to provide insights on levels of street life in  the company launched vantagelive which allows users to view intersection activity by automatically collecting and analyzing vehicle bicycle and pedestrian data on a continuous basis  research and developmentedit september  iteris inc announced the new webbased software ipems lite for arterial and freeway applications with an instant analysis and visualization of big data in traffic conditions such as speed and congestions may  iteris inc cooperated with inrix to integrate inrix’s realtime and historical traffic information with iterispem after the integration iterispems could collect traffic data information across all major highways and arterial roads for better evaluation abilities iteris has also collaborated with conservis to provide weather data and analytics to farmers  awardsedit  asce’s award for the outstanding private sector civil engineering project for its contribution to metro orange line extension  iteris received the project achievement award to by cmaa southern california chapter for the metro orange line extension  iteris won the one of the best in the west by the american association of state highway and transportation officials aashto for the i north designbuild project  iteris won the next downtown a sustainable vision for downtown la by the american planning association apa los angeles section referencesedit  iteris to acquire meridian environmental technologies   business summary   form q company acquisition   company mission and history   company full description   year of the bicycle signals iteris release of vantage® smartcycle™   iteris launches pedtrax computer vision for smarter crosswalks   httpwwwbusinesswirecomnewshomeeniterislaunchessaassolutioncollectprocessanalyze  missing or empty title help  iteris introduces ipems lite software to better know your roadway network   iteris collaborates with inrix to provide actionable traffic intelligence   httpswwwiteriscomaboutnewsiterisandconserviscorppartnertoprovidedecisionsupportanalyticsforfarmmanagement  missing or empty title help  the asce region  board of governors is pleased to announce the  individual and project awards   project award winners pdf   a b awards  recognitiona  external linksedit official website retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitleiterisoldid categories construction and civil engineering companies of the united statesintelligent transportation system sensortechnology companies based in the greater los angeles areacompanies based in santa ana californiaconstruction and civil engineering companies established in transport companies established in  establishments in californiacompanies listed on nasdaqhidden categories pages with citations lacking titlespages with citations having bare urlsarticles containing potentially dated statements from december all articles containing potentially dated statementspages using infobox company with unsupported parametersofficial website not in wikidata navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article talk variants views read edit view history more search navigation main pagecontentsfeatured contentcurrent eventsrandom articledonate to wikipediawikipedia store interaction helpabout wikipediacommunity portalrecent changescontact page tools what links hererelated changesupload file